cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.CV 

This paper is about learning to control a drone, which is a robotic system. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also uses deep learning techniques to learn a probabilistic model of the drone dynamics, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also mentions that the controller and value function are optimized using stochastic analytic gradients, which is a technique commonly used in control systems, suggesting that it could belong to cs.SY (Systems and Control). Finally, the paper mentions the use of raw sensory input, which could suggest that it belongs to cs.CV (Computer Vision) as well.
